{"tid":1093160,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》深夜預售觸發全城搶飛熱潮　IMAX門票最搶手最貴炒至750蚊一張","createTime":"2019-04-05T11:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T11:45:57.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3687c2bb313349f645c133527f18cb2e648f21cc","tid":1093160,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T11:39:50.000Z","msg":"Marvel超級英雄新作《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》（Avengers：Endgame）被視為本年度最矚目電影，香港上映日期已定本月24日，今日開賣已有多場出現滿座情況，尖沙嘴UA iSQUARE於開畫日早上8時15分有首場IMAX放映，早場票價定為260港元，至今日中午已差不多賣清，而銅鑼灣UA Cine Times更加開大清早6時場次，雖然是2D上映（票價125港元），但也售出大半數門票。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190405/large/1554442005_98f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190405%2Flarge%2F1554442005_98f3.jpg&h=3b491bbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nUA iSQUARE於開畫日首場IMAX已差不多賣清。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190405/large/1554442005_d2f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190405%2Flarge%2F1554442005_d2f5.jpg&h=592e12d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nUA Cine Times於清晨6時的2D場次，門票也賣得七七八八。<br />\n<br />\n不過粉絲昨晚開始排隊，目的是希望奪得開畫日首批觀眾限定紀念戲票；據香港迪士尼消息指，凡於網上或到戲院購買《復仇者4》在4月24日早上9時前場次之戲票，即可憑票於開畫日向戲院職員換領紀念戲票。一張正式戲票，可換領紀念戲票一張，獲大批影迷於首日即踴躍搶飛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190405/large/1554442007_32e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190405%2Flarge%2F1554442007_32e3.jpg&h=97155a78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人把限定紀念戲票抬高至750港元一張。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190405/large/1554442007_eee7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190405%2Flarge%2F1554442007_eee7.jpg&h=d89cded4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩張IMAX連位也被炒至1,000港元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1C4Wh9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1C4Wh9c.jpg&h=3b4cbcf6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n《復仇者4》開畫日早上9時前的入場人士可換取紀念票一張。<br />\n<br />\n《復仇者4》掀起的搶飛熱正一發不可收拾，今日已有人把開畫日戲票放於網上炒賣，旺角UA Cine Moko IMAX的早上7時45分場次，連同限定紀念戲票，已被抬高至最貴750港元一張。同時，有人把元朗MY CINEMA YOHO MALL兩張連座的IMAX普通戲票，由原價250港元一張，炒至1,000港元兩張。"},{"pid":"439047ee49f352b29079d7a335acadca84891ea4","tid":1093160,"uid":191650,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T11:41:03.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係乜都炒"},{"pid":"e7e59b323334fc4add1460c49ba584a9694b7ce4","tid":1093160,"uid":129169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T11:41:53.000Z","msg":"有人買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330770a05c4bd59575b6312a0197c8c46d98c6d4","tid":1093160,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T11:43:10.000Z","msg":"其實張紀念飛咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b91b950a89b5b8f94fdce6ea338bbdd0f13512","tid":1093160,"uid":6017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7e59b323334fc4add1460c49ba584a9694b7ce4","tid":1093160,"uid":129169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T11:41:53.000Z","msg":"有人買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T11:45:57.000Z","msg":"實有傻閪買架"}]}